Production Checklist Cheat Sheet. Visual checklist with 7 categories as columns: DESIGN, DEVELOPMENT, SECURITY, PRODUCTION, EVALUATION, GOVERNANCE, COST. Each column has 5-6 checkbox items with icons. Anti-Pattern column on right with 10 red X items. Tool Recommendations row at bottom. Color coding: Green=Done, Yellow=In Progress, Red=Missing. German labels, printable poster format.